------
gcc 5
------
sudo apt install vim

sudo vim /etc/apt/sources.list
[Add the below two lines in the end]
deb http://dk.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ xenial main
deb http://dk.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ xenial universe
Note: How to edit in vim:
	I	Enter into edit mode
	Esc	Exit from edit mode
	:wq	Save the file with all changes
	Copy-paste commands are same as that of terminal


sudo apt update

sudo apt install gcc-5 g++-5

sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/gcc gcc /usr/bin/gcc-5 100
sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/g++ g++ /usr/bin/g++-5 100


-----------
python 2.7
-----------
sudo apt install python2.7

sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python2.7 100


------------
scons 3.0.5
------------
Download:
https://sourceforge.net/projects/scons/files/scons/

Install:
[Go to the scons directory]
sudo python setup.py install --standard-lib


------------
swig 3.0.12
------------
Download
https://sourceforge.net/projects/swig/files/swig/

Install:
[Go to the swig directory]
./configure
make
sudo make install
